1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 22=

21
00:01:27,150 --> 00:01:28,200
Cuiwei.

22
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,070
What brings you here?

23
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:31,920
Consort Lan wants the pastries you make.

24
00:01:33,230 --> 00:01:34,680
What does she want?

25
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,870
I'll make it right away.

26
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,760
Our Consort is picky.

27
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,840
She wants them freshly made.

28
00:01:39,150 --> 00:01:40,230
Miss Ye Jin.

29
00:01:40,230 --> 00:01:42,070
Why not make it in our palace's kitchen?

30
00:01:42,510 --> 00:01:43,350
Alright.

31
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:44,710
Please.

32
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,680
Your Highness.

33
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,800
You're back.

34
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:37,310
Why did Consort Lan summon you tonight?

35
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,120
Nothing.

36
00:02:40,470 --> 00:02:41,590
I'm going to my room.

37
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,800
Wait.

38
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,470
Just look at your face,

39
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,360
I can tell something happened.

40
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,430
Why don't you

41
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:05,310
try to trust me?

42
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:16,120
Greetings, Your Majesty.

43
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:17,870
Rise, everyone.

44
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,430
Thank you, Your Majesty.

45
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:28,520
Concubine Hui,
you grow heavier by the day.

46
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:31,240
No need to come to
Cining Palace to greet me.

47
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,120
Thank you for your kindness,
Your Majesty.

48
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:36,520
But the Imperial Physician said
I must walk daily.

49
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:38,000
I'm fine.

50
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,630
Since you must walk daily,

51
00:03:39,910 --> 00:03:41,520
you can walk in the Imperial Garden.

52
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,840
Stay away from crowds.

53
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,470
Yes, I understand.

54
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,640
Enough.

55
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,430
You've greeted me today.

56
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:49,960
You may leave.

57
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:52,240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

58
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,360
Your Majesty.

59
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,310
I accuse

60
00:03:55,470 --> 00:03:57,750
Concubine Hui of murdering Lady Qiu Yu.

61
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,800
What did you say?

62
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:01,430
During the selection a year ago,

63
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,870
Lady Qiu Yu died suddenly in her room.

64
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:06,590
Back then,
all believed Ye Jin was the killer.

65
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,520
Later, Ye Jin was proven innocent.

66
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,680
Yet the real killer was never found.

67
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:13,120
I have physical evidence now.

68
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:15,280
It is enough to prove
who the real killer was.

69
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:16,470
That person...

70
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:17,590
is Concubine Hui.

71
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:20,830
The harem was just peaceful.

72
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,430
And you stir trouble again.

73
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,390
Lady Xiao, you should understand that

74
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:27,430
if you have no solid proof,

75
00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:29,070
you'll be charged

76
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,600
with disrespecting a superior.

77
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,360
I have proof.

78
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,000
This pearl hairpin is the proof.

79
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:36,240
This is indeed
Concubine Hui's pearl hairpin.

80
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:37,560
She wore it every day

81
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,630
before the selection.

82
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,920
When Qiu Yu died,

83
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:43,480
the coroner said her fingertips
were covered in blood marks.

84
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:45,240
It meant she'd grabbed

85
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,800
something tightly.

86
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,560
But this hairpin wasn't found then.

87
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,070
Later,

88
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,680
on her seventh memorial day,

89
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:53,950
I accidentally found

90
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,680
this pearl hairpin

91
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,870
in the crack of her bed.

92
00:04:57,430 --> 00:04:58,270
And I just learned

93
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:01,070
it's Concubine Hui's old hairpin.

94
00:05:01,270 --> 00:05:02,630
If you have no other proof,

95
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,040
with this alone,

96
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,630
how can you convict her?

97
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,560
Your Majesty,

98
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,630
I'm willing to give witness testimony.

99
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,240
On that day when Qiu Yu was harmed,

100
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,750
Concubine Hui did indeed go out.

101
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:17,040
She came back looking terrified.

102
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:18,160
If that's true,

103
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,190
why didn't you speak up then?

104
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:22,950
That day, I had many doubts,

105
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:25,430
but I'd just entered the palace,

106
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:26,630
so I didn't dare to speak.

107
00:05:27,190 --> 00:05:29,240
Now I truly cannot sleep at night.

108
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,430
Nightmares have been clinging to me.

109
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:32,560
So I chose to tell the truth.

110
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:34,240
Concubine Hui.

111
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:35,920
What do you say to that?

112
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,000
Your Majesty,

113
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,080
I...

114
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,630
didn't kill her.

115
00:05:46,630 --> 00:05:48,000
What do you think?

116
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:49,800
As Your Majesty said,

117
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,920
this is an old case.

118
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,720
And both witness and physical evidence
are doubtful.

119
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,430
I dare not judge rashly.

120
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:58,310
But we must be cautious.

121
00:05:58,830 --> 00:05:59,920
I think

122
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,750
this case must be fully investigated.

123
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:02,830
Fully investigated?

124
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:04,750
If Your Majesty trusts me,

125
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,360
let me handle this case.

126
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,040
I'll give you a full account.

127
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:15,360
I'm willing to
help Consort De investigate.

128
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:17,830
That couldn't be better.

129
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,950
Except Concubine Hui and Attendant Liu,

130
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:30,560
all other selected women have alibis.

131
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,270
Concubine Hui.

132
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,160
Think carefully.

133
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:37,630
Do you have anyone
to prove you were elsewhere?

134
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,040
Your Ladyship,

135
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:42,120
I

136
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:43,670
don't.

137
00:06:43,950 --> 00:06:49,000
Then you can't deny
involvement in Qiu Yu's death.

138
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,800
I'll say it again.

139
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,440
I

140
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:53,870
didn't kill her.

141
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,800
The witness and evidence are clear.

142
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:59,040
How can you prove your innocence?

143
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:03,390
Even if all evidence points to her,

144
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:08,070
it doesn't mean she's the killer.

145
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:13,390
Greetings, Consort Lan.

146
00:07:13,390 --> 00:07:14,390
Greetings, Consort De.

147
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,640
Rise.

148
00:07:15,650 --> 00:07:16,520
Thank you, Your Ladyship.

149
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:21,360
Besides the ladies here,

150
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,040
many maids and eunuchs
lived in Chuxiu Palace.

151
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,830
If we retry this case,

152
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,750
all those maids and eunuchs

153
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,430
must be questioned again.

154
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,630
Furthermore,

155
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,920
the ladies here today

156
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,800
may not be telling the truth.

157
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:37,360
Who can prove they aren't lying?

158
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:38,910
Ye Jin.

159
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,390
What are you saying?

160
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:42,720
Today,

161
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,510
I also have an item

162
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:50,800
to show all of you.

163
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,120
I was the first to arrive

164
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:05,160
when Qiu Yu was killed.

165
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:09,040
This was found at the crime scene.

166
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,950
If we follow this logic
to find the killer,

167
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:14,680
I think the owner of this hairpin

168
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,310
is the killer.

169
00:08:17,190 --> 00:08:18,390
Isn't this hairpin

170
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,430
Attendant Liu's?

171
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:24,120
Attendant Liu, you have no alibi.

172
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,800
How do you explain this?

173
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:27,960
I...

174
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,680
I was sleeping in my room.

175
00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:31,960
Does anyone confirm this?

176
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,030
His Majesty arrives.

177
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,000
Rise, my ladies.

178
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,750
Thank you, Your Majesty.

179
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,280
Preposterous!

180
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,440
An old case

181
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,960
is dragged up with no proof

182
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,720
and disturbs the peace of the harem.

183
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:57,670
Help me, Your Majesty.

184
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,870
Attendant Liu

185
00:08:58,870 --> 00:09:01,000
threatened my parents' lives

186
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,000
to make me frame Concubine Hui.

187
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,030
I didn't!

188
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,360
That pearl hairpin
was given to me by you.

189
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,790
The false accusation today

190
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:11,320
was also your idea.

191
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:13,480
Lady Xiao framed me!

192
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:15,000
I'm innocent!

193
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,960
An investigation will tell.

194
00:09:16,770 --> 00:09:17,640
Guards!

195
00:09:17,670 --> 00:09:19,320
Take Attendant Liu to
the Punishment Office.

196
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:20,790
If the framing is confirmed,

197
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:21,870
beat her to death!

198
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,390
Save me, Consort Lan!

199
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:26,230
It was you who made me...

200
00:09:26,230 --> 00:09:27,090
Nonsense!

201
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,160
Guards!

202
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,510
Beat her to death!

203
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:30,630
Guards!

204
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,560
Take her away.

205
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:32,540
Consort Lan!

206
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:34,600
I did it all for you!

207
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:35,870
Your Majesty!

208
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:37,480
Your Majesty!

209
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:44,920
Your Majesty.

210
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:55,000
Guards! Summon the Imperial Physician.

211
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:55,960
Yes.

212
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:16,390
What exactly happened today?

213
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,550
Liu Mei did plan this.

214
00:10:19,270 --> 00:10:20,750
But she's not smart enough

215
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:22,910
to make such a detailed plan.

216
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,840
The 14th Prince investigated for me.

217
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:26,390
There's someone else behind this.

218
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:27,550
It's Yunxi.

219
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,030
Yunxi?

220
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:31,440
I've done nothing to her.

221
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,630
Why would she hurt me?

222
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,510
Out of jealousy.

223
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:37,790
And to please her master,

224
00:10:37,790 --> 00:10:38,960
Consort Lan.

225
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,390
This is a cruel trick.

226
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,550
The case is old,

227
00:10:46,550 --> 00:10:48,840
and there's not enough proof
to convict me,

228
00:10:49,030 --> 00:10:50,320
but because of that,

229
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,960
it's hard to clear my name.

230
00:10:52,390 --> 00:10:53,230
Exactly.

231
00:10:54,030 --> 00:10:55,790
You're carrying a prince now,

232
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:57,750
and His Majesty favors you.

233
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,750
This won't kill you.

234
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:02,960
But the label of murder suspect

235
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,790
will stain you forever.

236
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,870
Your rank in the harem

237
00:11:07,030 --> 00:11:08,600
will never rise higher.

238
00:11:09,030 --> 00:11:10,910
Even if you have the prince,

239
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:12,600
you may not raise him yourself.

240
00:11:13,030 --> 00:11:13,870
In this way,

241
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,550
Consort Lan will easily

242
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:18,960
get rid of you, her biggest threat.

243
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:20,600
How vicious.

244
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:30,390
Thank you for saving me today.

245
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,510
Otherwise,

246
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:34,200
I'd be doomed.

247
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:35,790
Between you and me,

248
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:37,550
don't be so formal.

249
00:11:38,390 --> 00:11:39,510
Just use today's

250
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,390
scare as an excuse to claim illness,

251
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:44,200
stay in your palace
and rest well for the baby.

252
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,030
Now that Consort De has risen,

253
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:48,080
Consort Lan has a new rival.

254
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:50,320
She won't focus on you for now.

255
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,750
But my baby

256
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,960
will be born in a few months.

257
00:11:57,550 --> 00:11:59,630
What if she harms me during labor?

258
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,280
Ye Jin,

259
00:12:02,630 --> 00:12:03,630
I'm so scared.

260
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:06,910
Then will you stay with me?

261
00:12:07,270 --> 00:12:08,390
You'll stay with me.

262
00:12:08,510 --> 00:12:09,360
Right?

263
00:12:09,750 --> 00:12:10,590
Of course.

264
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:12,440
I'll be with you, I swear.

265
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:13,910
No matter what happens,

266
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,630
I'll be right by your side.

267
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:20,390
I'll never forget your kindness.

268
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,750
Alright.

269
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,510
Let's go back to the palace.

270
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,150
Is Consort Lan...

271
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,680
alright?

272
00:12:42,430 --> 00:12:43,270
Your Majesty.

273
00:12:43,270 --> 00:12:44,320
Consort Lan

274
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,550
has a pregnancy pulse!

275
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,270
A pregnancy pulse?

276
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,720
Consort Lan...

277
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,150
is with child.

278
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,160
Mother.

279
00:13:20,030 --> 00:13:20,870
What's wrong?

280
00:13:25,510 --> 00:13:26,440
Consort Lan is pregnant.

281
00:13:28,790 --> 00:13:31,360
She hurt her health years ago.

282
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:34,440
All these years,
she's had no sign of a child.

283
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:36,870
Why is she pregnant suddenly?

284
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:38,200
Could it be that

285
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,480
the diagnosis was wrong?

286
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:42,840
Physician Zheng and Physician Zhang
are experts.

287
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,000
They both checked her pulse.

288
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,510
So they can't be wrong.

289
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:47,630
Mm.

290
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:50,030
Then what will you do

291
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,390
with

292
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:53,840
the Consort Lan's child?

293
00:13:55,510 --> 00:13:56,390
Since it's here,

294
00:13:57,020 --> 00:13:58,000
it's my flesh and blood.

295
00:13:58,790 --> 00:13:59,630
I

296
00:13:59,870 --> 00:14:01,390
want the child to be born safely.

297
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:04,150
You've grown up.

298
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:06,000
If you've made up your mind,

299
00:14:06,150 --> 00:14:07,600
then arrange it properly.

300
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:09,480
I shall take my leave now.

301
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,240
My son.

302
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,480
What do you need, mother?

303
00:14:15,790 --> 00:14:18,000
Stay and dine with me.

304
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:21,390
It's been so long since we sat down

305
00:14:21,390 --> 00:14:22,670
and had a real talk.

306
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:30,630
I hear some officials
in the southwestern frontier

307
00:14:30,630 --> 00:14:31,840
are bleeding the people dry,

308
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:34,030
driving the Miao people
to rise up in revolt.

309
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,320
They have already seized many places.

310
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,750
You're well-informed.

311
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:41,270
You've held meetings
with ministers for days.

312
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,630
With such a stir,

313
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,150
how could I not know?

314
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:46,000
I'm old

315
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,670
and have ignored state affairs
for years.

316
00:14:48,150 --> 00:14:49,550
But with a matter this grave,

317
00:14:50,270 --> 00:14:52,510
you should have informed me.

318
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:56,030
You should rest peacefully now.

319
00:14:57,030 --> 00:14:59,390
It would be unfilial to

320
00:14:59,700 --> 00:15:00,790
trouble you with state affairs.

321
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,960
Consort Lan's brother
once guarded the southwest

322
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:06,080
and dealt with the Miao tribe.

323
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,440
Logically,

324
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:09,480
he's best suited to lead troops
to suppress the rebellion.

325
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:12,440
But since he returned to the capital,

326
00:15:12,790 --> 00:15:13,840
he's claimed to be ill

327
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:14,680
and stayed at home.

328
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,480
I summoned him many times,

329
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:17,670
but he refused.

330
00:15:17,910 --> 00:15:20,550
Are there no other generals?

331
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:26,150
The Lan clan
has held great power for years.

332
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:29,080
Many generals are their allies.

333
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,510
If we rush into war now,

334
00:15:30,550 --> 00:15:31,390
it'll be

335
00:15:31,670 --> 00:15:33,550
hard to distance ourselves
from the Lan clan.

336
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:36,960
Then use your brother.

337
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:38,550
Back when the southwest was pacified,

338
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:40,080
14th Prince was also in the army

339
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:42,080
and had dealings with the Miao people.

340
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:43,510
He's your own blood brother.

341
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:45,030
Utterly loyal to you.

342
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:46,670
If he leads the army,

343
00:15:46,670 --> 00:15:48,240
it's the safest choice.

344
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,510
(Isn't the 14th Prince in the novel)

345
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:53,840
(fated to die in the southwest?)

346
00:15:59,260 --> 00:16:01,700
♪I am but an outsider♪

347
00:16:01,740 --> 00:16:03,900
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

348
00:16:04,140 --> 00:16:08,180
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

349
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:12,420
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

350
00:16:16,700 --> 00:16:19,940
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

351
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:23,500
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

352
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:26,020
♪I know how this story ends♪

353
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:30,580
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

354
00:16:30,900 --> 00:16:35,020
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

355
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:43,300
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

356
00:16:43,300 --> 00:16:46,580
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

357
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:49,860
♪A history that no one can search♪

358
00:16:50,100 --> 00:16:53,380
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

359
00:16:53,420 --> 00:16:55,180
♪I am but an outsider♪

360
00:16:55,180 --> 00:16:57,420
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

361
00:16:57,420 --> 00:17:01,460
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

362
00:17:01,460 --> 00:17:06,140
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

363
00:17:10,060 --> 00:17:13,460
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

364
00:17:13,460 --> 00:17:16,820
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

365
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:19,300
♪I know how this story ends♪

366
00:17:19,300 --> 00:17:23,460
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

367
00:17:23,460 --> 00:17:26,740
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

368
00:17:26,740 --> 00:17:30,540
♪Please forget me and move on♪

369
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:36,780
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

370
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:48,300
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

371
00:17:51,860 --> 00:18:01,580
♪When do I finally wake♪
